WEBVTT

00:07.007 --> 00:08.575
[Noah] Previously on The Affair...

00:08.575 --> 00:10.043
You have chosen to divorce

00:10.043 --> 00:12.412
in what I like to call a humane way.

00:12.412 --> 00:14.147
[Noah] All I want is
joint custody of the kids.

00:14.147 --> 00:15.249
[Jeremy] Do you have a
physical space for them

00:15.249 --> 00:17.184
to live in at the moment?

00:17.184 --> 00:18.752
As soon as my book is finished,
I'll get the rest of my advance,

00:18.752 --> 00:20.320
and then I'll rent an apartment in the city

00:20.320 --> 00:21.555
that's big enough for all of us.

00:21.555 --> 00:22.723
So you wanna go with this ending instead?

00:22.723 --> 00:24.091
I think it's really powerful.

00:24.091 --> 00:25.425
What can I tell ya? I don't agree.

00:25.425 --> 00:26.727
[Helen] Are you living with her?

00:26.727 --> 00:28.128
[Noah] No, Helen, I'm not.

00:28.128 --> 00:29.730
I don't want her anywhere near my kids.

00:29.730 --> 00:32.198
Well, you might not get to
have everything you want, Helen.

00:32.198 --> 00:34.101
I always thought I'd be planning a wedding

00:34.101 --> 00:35.602
for the two of you after graduation.

00:35.602 --> 00:37.571
I just can't believe I finally got her.

00:37.571 --> 00:39.439
- Stop talking.
- Who the fuck are you?

00:39.439 --> 00:41.108
I'm his lawyer, Jon Gottlief.

00:41.108 --> 00:43.110
Any decisions concerning my husband's

00:43.110 --> 00:44.611
legal representation need to go through me.

00:44.611 --> 00:46.513
[justice] The state of
New York hereby charges you

00:46.513 --> 00:48.248
with obstruction of justice,

00:48.248 --> 00:50.217
leaving the scene of an accident,

00:50.217 --> 00:52.219
and vehicular homicide.

00:52.219 --> 00:53.720
It's a horrible thing to love a writer.

00:53.720 --> 00:56.156
All their secret worlds, their fantasies.

00:56.156 --> 00:58.125
[chuckles] Have you read it?

00:58.125 --> 01:00.494
[Alison] Not yet. No. [chuckles]

01:00.494 --> 01:02.396
Yvonne, meet your new assistant.

01:02.396 --> 01:04.498
Good.

01:04.498 --> 01:05.732
What are you doing here?

01:05.732 --> 01:07.734
Relax, I just came to bring you your stuff.

01:07.734 --> 01:10.237
Almost forgot the most
important piece of the puzzle.

01:10.237 --> 01:12.406
I'm sure you didn't mean
to leave that behind.

