03:44.091 --> 03:46.059
You're a real sphinx, you know that?

03:47.994 --> 03:50.664
Is that a compliment?

03:50.664 --> 03:53.333
No. [chuckles]

03:58.338 --> 04:00.040
I'm gonna jump in the pool before dinner.

04:00.040 --> 04:01.441
Go for it.

04:01.441 --> 04:02.509
Why don't you come with me?

04:02.509 --> 04:05.645
No, no, I'm okay.

04:05.645 --> 04:08.014
You haven't got in the
pool once since we got here.

04:10.283 --> 04:14.020
Come on, it's saltwater. It feels amazing.

04:14.020 --> 04:16.156
I don't feel like swimming.

04:21.094 --> 04:23.263
And what if I drag you there?

04:23.263 --> 04:25.232
- Drag you there.
- No, Noah, stop! Noah!

04:25.232 --> 04:27.400
- Drag you in the pool.
- Noah! No, I said stop!

04:33.607 --> 04:36.343
I just don't want to. Okay?

04:38.044 --> 04:40.280
Okay, no problem.

04:49.623 --> 04:52.692
[♪ soft music ♪]

04:52.692 --> 04:56.692
